                                    <div class="faq-section" style="margin-top: 40px;">
                                        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                                        <h3>Should I pick WordPress or a custom-coded site?</h3>
                                        <p>WordPress for content-heavy SME sites where you'll edit pages weekly. Custom-coded (Next.js / Astro / Laravel) for SaaS, e-commerce-with-custom-flows, or sites with heavy integrations. Most Chennai studios are competent in both; ask which they recommend and why.</p>
                                        <h3>Do Chennai studios handle multi-language for GCC / EU markets?</h3>
                                        <p>Yes. Tamil + English + Hindi domestically; Arabic + RTL + French + Spanish for GCC/EU clients. WPML, Polylang, or i18next routes are all common. Plan for 8–12% added cost per language.</p>
                                        <h3>How long does a typical SME website take?</h3>
                                        <p>4–6 weeks for a 15–25 page lead-gen site, including discovery, copy, design, dev, content upload and launch. Pure design + dev (with copy and content provided by client) can ship in 3 weeks.</p>
                                        <h3>Can Chennai studios handle US/EU clients with timezone overlap?</h3>
                                        <p>Yes. Most Chennai studios offer a 4-hour overlap window — Chennai 5pm IST = London 12pm GMT = NY 7am EST. Daily standup at 6:30pm IST works well for most US East Coast clients.</p>
                                        <h3>What's the realistic SEO contribution of a new website?</h3>
                                        <p>A well-built new website lifts organic traffic 25–60% in months 3–6 just from technical SEO + Core Web Vitals improvements. Beyond that needs ongoing content + backlinks (a separate retainer at &#8377;30k–&#8377;1L/month).</p>
                                        <h3>Do you handle hosting and AMC?</h3>
                                        <p>Yes — we deploy on AWS / GCP / DigitalOcean / managed WP (Cloudways / Kinsta). AMC contracts cover security patches, plugin updates, backups, uptime monitoring, and minor content edits. Typical AMC: &#8377;6k–&#8377;25k/month based on scope.</p>
